oai_dc:dc.dc:title: Liberty Bowl bids
oai_dc:dc.dc:subject: Memphis Park Commission; Liberty Bowl; business; food;
oai_dc:dc.dc:description: A chart showing bids from various companies for assorted concession items at the Liberty Bowl, including ice, peanuts, hot dogs, buns, hamburger meat, pizza, cups, cigarettes, candy bars and other sandwiches.
